description:
Make an impact with these rare cosmetic items as you attempt to chomp any challengers standing between you and the title of Chomp Champ!

This PAC includes:
- 1 Unicorn - Rare (body)
- 1 Crown (head)
- 1 Pompadour (head)
- 1 Punk (head)
- 1 Googly Glasses (face)
- 1 Retro Glasses (face)
- 1 Cherry Chomp (icon)
name: PAC-MAN Mega Tunnel Battle: Chomp Champs - Chomp Challengers PAC
